# Force LF line endings on every checkout, including Windows.
#
# rustfmt and `cargo fmt --all --check` reject CRLF-terminated source
# files; Windows runners on GitHub Actions checkout with CRLF by
# default, which made the CI matrix red after B3.7.
#
# `text=auto` lets git decide if a path is text; `eol=lf` overrides the
# platform default so working trees on Windows end up LF too.

* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary fixtures must not be touched by line-ending normalisation.
tests/fixtures/** binary
*.png binary
*.so  binary
*.dll binary
*.exe binary
*.o   binary
